      },
      "date": "2018-08-02 22:43:18.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n(1 comment)\n\nback in April when I thought about it - I did not see any relevant interactions.\n\nThese locks we are working on here are always on a file the server knows about. Current wbc implementation is for files server does not know about. Even later ther should not be a problem because we would be getting exclusive locks anyway.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
